00:37:42.820 --> 00:37:45.402
You know, it's interesting
in Europe, the way that,

00:37:45.402 --> 00:37:49.290
at least in orthopedics, when
they take care of a child,

00:37:49.290 --> 00:37:51.050
say that, a hip problem.

00:37:51.050 --> 00:37:53.790
So an orthopedic surgeon
will take care of the newborn

00:37:53.790 --> 00:37:57.320
hip with DDH and will also
put the total joint in.

00:37:57.320 --> 00:37:59.200
They take care of it
through the whole lifespan

00:37:59.200 --> 00:38:00.600
and we don't even do that
in the United States.

00:38:00.600 --> 00:38:01.973
We stop, the same thing.

00:38:01.973 --> 00:38:05.090
We have adult and pediatric providers.

00:38:05.090 --> 00:38:09.590
And so, as you transition
through life, these are my last,

00:38:09.590 --> 00:38:10.980
I'm back to cartoon, so now I can

