00:38:19.920 --> 00:38:21.290
You have all the agencies.

00:38:21.290 --> 00:38:22.990
You have CC, and all
these, CCS, what does all

00:38:22.990 --> 00:38:23.880
this stuff mean?

00:38:23.880 --> 00:38:26.190
MediCal, all these things.

00:38:26.190 --> 00:38:29.410
You have all these, people
are talking about PDAs

00:38:29.410 --> 00:38:31.900
and necrotizing enterocolitis
and all these words

00:38:31.900 --> 00:38:33.525
you've never heard of.

00:38:33.525 --> 00:38:35.530
Your family's thrown into an upheaval.

00:38:35.530 --> 00:38:38.870
You have other children and
then you have financial,

00:38:38.870 --> 00:38:41.040
you know, financial
problems on top of that.

00:38:41.040 --> 00:38:42.841
You have to buy a van, you
have to buy these things

00:38:42.841 --> 00:38:45.360
and then as they get older
you have to worry about

00:38:45.360 --> 00:38:46.392
what they do for leisure.

00:38:46.392 --> 00:38:49.035
You have to do this IEP for, I mean,

00:38:49.035 --> 00:38:50.550
this is technology.

00:38:50.550 --> 00:38:54.652
So buying those iPads, no
one's paying for those.

00:38:54.652 --> 00:38:59.652
Getting the, your big van
to get people somewhere.

