Education, I had to do an
IAP every year for my son,

00:39:04.482 --> 00:39:07.060
or I mean I had to, I had to
threaten to sue the school

00:39:07.060 --> 00:39:10.000
district every year 'til he
graduated from high school.

00:39:10.000 --> 00:39:11.110
I mean, I mean, seriously.

00:39:11.110 --> 00:39:13.680
I mean, I just bring in
the law and I drop it down.

00:39:13.680 --> 00:39:14.870
I go, I know how to read the law,

00:39:14.870 --> 00:39:17.870
and I got to go, it's the same
principle, same everything.

00:39:17.870 --> 00:39:19.270
So think of parents that aren't

00:39:19.270 --> 00:39:20.920
sophisticated how hard that is.

00:39:20.920 --> 00:39:23.470
And then, I'm not saying
I'm sophisticated,

00:39:23.470 --> 00:39:25.810
but I know how to read the law, and then,

00:39:25.810 --> 00:39:27.930
and then social interactions,
how do your kids

00:39:27.930 --> 00:39:30.290
have to, how do you
get them to have be out

00:39:30.290 --> 00:39:31.123
with their friends?

00:39:31.123 --> 00:39:33.483
I mean, that's, you
know, it's really hard.

00:39:34.780 --> 00:39:37.000
Then, you know, when I talked about jobs,

00:39:37.000 --> 00:39:38.070
